<span id="an_7:22">7:22</span> one male of the goats for a sin-offering;

<span id="an_7:23">7:23</span> and for the sacrifice of peace-offerings,
two oxen, five rams, five he-goats, five he-lambs a year old: this was
the oblation of Nethanel the son of Zuar.

<span id="an_7:24">7:24</span> On the third day Eliab the son of Helon,
prince of the children of Zebulun.:

<span id="an_7:25">7:25</span> his oblation was one silver platter, the
