<span id="an_7:34">7:34</span> one male of the goats for a sin-offering;

<span id="an_7:35">7:35</span> and for the sacrifice of peace-offerings,
two oxen, five rams, five he-goats, five he-lambs a year old: this was
the oblation of Elizur the son of Shedeur.

<span id="an_7:36">7:36</span> On the fifth day Shelumiel the son of
Zurishaddai, prince of the children of Simeon:

<span id="an_7:37">7:37</span> his oblation was one silver platter, the
